metadata.description: Doodle Ducks Genesis is the OG collection of the Doodle Ducks. Doodle Ducks is the most anticipated crossover project between two extremey successful NFT projects, Doodles and SupDucks. Some say god didn't make anything perfect, this doesn't apply to Doodle Ducks - Doodle Ducks' art is put together with the features of two most eye-appealing collections in NFT history. Doodle Ducks is not just art, Doodle Ducks is a movement.
metadata.name: Doodle Duck Gen #1
